{"type": "article", "id": 2445, "title": "Babilus 花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-19T10:26:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232425R65fNdEirKh8b2C3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自以色列特拉维夫的设计师Nir Meiri，受到古城建筑物、寺庙以及祭坛的影响，用竹子、玻璃以及人造石打造了一系列花瓶，每一种材质都是一层一层堆叠起来，形成了一组丰富动感的纹理效果，描绘了古城的轮廓，呈参差不齐的阶梯型形状。这款多材料打造而成的花瓶有 4 个不同的尺寸，用于单个花的花瓶、用于大花束的花瓶或是适用于小盆栽的花瓶。这个系列的作品最近正在伦敦设计节的 <a href=\"http://www.19greekstreet.com/\" target=\"_blank\">19greekstreet 画廊</a>展出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232422fbnKistjY82ukNpQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232423IFufyhsKoURTYpnX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232423lZk4V2z7Tca6G8do.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232424NX3JnadYMpvZ5i8t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}